0He%20says%20he%20has%20a%20level%20of%20job%20satisfaction%20and%20flexibility%20that%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20ever%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20the%20freedom%2C%20but%20also%20having%20all%20that%20responsibility%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20is%20my%20business%20or%20all%20on%20me%20to%20get%20everything%20done%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20something%20that's%20very%20freeing%20in%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMendez%2C%2034%2C%20spoke%20with%20BI%20about%20scaling%20his%20business%2C%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D671675df9cb8747a5f6b7f819ce7d9e4aada7edd1122db3c7dccd73ffbe0393f%26postID%3D68224a2d956ea078b938f7d6%26postSlug%3Dtaskrabbit-earnings-monthly-quit-job-freelancer-hours-schedule-furniture-assembly-2025-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.taskrabbit.com%252Fprofile%252Flove%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20elite%20tasker%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20nearly%20perfect%20rating%20and%20more%20than%201%2C500%20reviews%2C%20and%20what%20his%20typical%20day%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220245f7c8-1617-47d6-898b-0c1823c8c51e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENiching%20down%20and%20scaling%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20can%20hire%20Taskrabbits%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20home%20tasks%2C%20and%20Mendez%20initially%20offered%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20services%3A%20moving%2C%20organizing%2C%20furniture%20assembly%2C%20deliveries%2C%20and%20heavy%20lifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20very%20first%20task%20was%20a%20cleaning%20gig%2C%20though%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20lasted%20too%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20tried%20to%20do%20as%20many%20as%20I%20could.%20I%20wanted%20to%20just%20feel%20out%20the%20app%20and%20see%20what%20it%20could%20offer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22michael%20taskrabbit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insi