%3E%26quot%3BI%20pay%20very%20little%20attention%20to%20where%20the%20founder%20has%20worked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20there's%20any%20correlation%20between%20being%20a%20star%20at%20a%20medium-sized%20or%20large%20company%20and%20being%20a%20seed-stage%20founder%20because%20it's%20such%20a%20different%20dynamic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22544518a0-b1d0-4656-b87a-79809861d95b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20for%20a%20'complete%20founding%20team'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20plenty%20of%20investors%20mythologize%20a%20single%20founder%20like%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20or%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Rajaram%20looks%20more%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20founding%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20a%20builder%20and%20a%20seller%2C%20a%20balance%20of%20product%20execution%20and%20go-to-market%20savvy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20builders%20who%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20go%20to%20market%2C%20don't%20have%20the%20commercial%20instinct%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20is%20you%20have%20both%20the%20commercial%20and%20the%20builder%20side%20represented%20on%20the%20founding%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20looks%20for%20%26quot%3Bfirst-principles%20thinking%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ability%20of%20a%20founder%20to%20reason%20through%20a%20problem%20from%20the%20ground%20up%2C%20rather%20than%20following%20conventional%20wisdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20approach%20led%20him%20to%20write%20one%20of%20the%20first%20checks%20to%20Printify%20founder%20James%20Berdigans%20in%202016.%20The%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.printful.com%2Fnews%2Fmerger%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emerged%20with%20its%20competitor%2C%20Printful%2C%20last%20year.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20passed%20on%20James%20in%20the%20pre-seed%2C%20but%20I%20was%20excited%20by%20the%20founder's%20depth%20of%20understanding%20and%20how%20much%20he%20knew%20about%20the%20failures%20of%20past%20attempts%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajaram%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERajaram%20is%20generous%20with%20his%20advice.%20On%20his%20website%2C%20he%20writes%20blog%20posts%20on%20product%20development%2C%20company%20culture%2C%20and%20strategy%2C%20among%20other%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20seed%20investing%20became%20more%20competitive%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Rajaram%20has%20tried%20to%20remain%20disciplined%20and%20avoid%20a%20sense%20of%20FOMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRounds%20were%20moving%20really%20fast%2C%20happening%20without%20any%20diligence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20be%20very%20thoughtful.%20I%20might%20miss%20a%20few%20great%20companies%2C%20but%20I%20also%20think%20a%20lot%20will%20flame%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERajaram%20has%20learned%20from%20experience%20that%20angel%20investing%20requires%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20fortitude%20because%20you're%20investing%20money%20in%20ideas%20with%20a%20high%20failure%20rate.%20Even%20the%20few%20who%20succeed%20against%20all%20odds%20can%20take%20over%20a%20decade%20to%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20focus%20too%20much%20on%20the%20financial%20returns%2C%20you'll%20be%20disappointed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20truly%20planting%20a%20seed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgokul-rajaram-seed-vc-investing-marathon-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747299601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681d1a29a466d2b74ab574c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgokul-rajaram-seed-vc-investing-marathon-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajaram's%20seed%20investing%20philosophy%20emphasizes%20finding%20founding%20teams%20with%20both%20commercial%20instinct%20and%20product%20execution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergm