d%20up%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20this%20week%20after%20the%20US%20and%20China%20agreed%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-trade-deal-agreement-slash-trump-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etemporary%20truce%20on%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20a%20top%20shipping%20executive%20warned%20that%20the%20rebound%20may%20not%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBookings%20for%20cargo%20capacity%20from%20China%20to%20the%20US%20have%20shot%20up%20this%20week%20after%20the%20two%20economic%20giants%20agreed%20to%20roll%20back%20tariffs%2C%20said%20Rolf%20Habben%20Jansen%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Hapag-Lloyd.%20The%20company%20is%20the%20world's%20fifth-largest%20shipping%20firm%20by%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20days%20that%20bookings%20have%20indeed%20been%20up%20more%20than%2050%25%20compared%20to%20what%20we%20saw%20the%20last%20four%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20first-quarter%20earnings%20call%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHabben%20Jansen%20said%20the%20rebound%20came%20after%20China-to-US%20container%20ship%20bookings%20crashed%2020-30%25%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20as%20Trump's%20145%25%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20took%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week's%20rapid%20turnaround%20followed%20the%20US%20slashing%20the%20combined%20tariff%20rate%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20to%2030%25%20for%2090%20days%20following%20the%20US%20and%20China's%20trade%20talks%20in%20Switzerland%20over%20the%20weekend.%20The%20new%20tariff%20rate%20took%20effect%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco-based%20container-tracking%20software%20provider%20Vizion%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20US-China%20container%20bookings%20surged%20277%25%20in%20the%20week%20from%20May%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20definitely%20starting%20to%20see%20the%20bookings%20return%20now%20that%20this%20temporary%20pause%20is%20in%20effect%2C%26quot