20cable%20company%20Discovery%20to%20form%20a%20new%20media%20conglomerate%2C%20which%20had%20even%20more%20exposure%20to%20the%20shrinking%20pay-TV%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery.%20David%20Zaslav%2C%20who'd%20run%20Discovery%20since%202006%2C%20was%20looking%20to%20make%20a%20splash%20and%20shake%20up%20Hollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20HBO's%20prestige%20fare%20and%20Discovery's%20guilty-pleasure%20shows%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%26quot%3BMy%20600-lb%20Life%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDr.%20Pimple%20Popper%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Zaslav%20dropped%20the%20HBO%20name%20from%20its%20streamer%20in%20hopes%20of%20being%20a%20something-for-everyone%20service%20like%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrand-recognition-streaming-netflix-amazon-disney-paramount-hbo-max-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econtroversial%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-co-ceo-says-max-should-have-been-hbo-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheavily%20criticized%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20some%2C%20though%20others%20argued%20the%20Max%20rebrand%20was%20necessary%20to%20protect%20the%20HBO%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD%20marked%20the%20rebrand%20to%20Max%20by%20swapping%20its%20purple%20gradient%20for%20a%20bright%20blue.%20Patrizio%20%26quot%3BPato%26quot%3B%20Spagnoletto%2C%20WBD's%20then-marketing%20chief%2C%20told%20Vulture%20that%20this%20change%20was%20%26quot%3Bintending%20to%20signal%20not%20just%20change%20from%20HBO%20Max%20of%20the%20purple%2C%20but%20a%20much%20more%20sustainable%20premium%20version%20of%20the%20service.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20had%20mixed%20results.%20It%20struggled%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstreaming-bundle-max-disney-hulu-warner-bros-discovery-wbd-netflix-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh%20cancellation%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20found%20success%